Egypt has accused Sudan of having orchestrated the 1995 failed
attempt on the life of the Egyptian president in Addis Ababa and
granting asylum to Egyptian extremists. Tensions escalated as
Sudan's demand to have larger Nile water quota sparked loud outcry
from Egypt. 
