<HEADLINE> HK, Shanghai to Discuss Housing Development </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, January 2 (Xinhua) -- Housing authorities in Hong
Kong and Shanghai will hold a conference in Shanghai from January
8 to 10 for professionals in the two cities to exchange views on
housing development, the Housing Authority (HA) of Hong Kong
announced here today.
